com.yworks.yfiles.utils

Interface IObservableCollection<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the items in the collection.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<T>, Iterable<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ObservableCollection

    public interface IObservableCollection<T>
extends Collection<T>
    The interface for a collection that will notify registered event handlers of changes to its contents.
    See Also:
    ObservableCollection
